<p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #666666;">You and your home are unique. A cookie-cutter experience for your solar installation won&rsquo;t provide you with choices so you can decide what&rsquo;s best for you, your family, and home. Nor will it provide you with the best value. At Direct Energy Solar, our customized process is tailored to each individual&mdash;this means we can maximize your energy production and you control how you pay for solar, so you receive greater financial returns and get the most benefits out of your solar home.</p>
